Drop Table [dbo].[F0902]
CREATE TABLE [dbo].[F0902]
(
    GBAID NCHAR(8) NULL, -- Account ID
    GBCTRY INT NULL, -- Century
    GBFY INT NULL, -- Fiscal Year
    GBFQ NCHAR(4) NULL, -- Fiscal Quarter (Obsolete)
    GBLT NCHAR(2) NULL, -- Ledger Types
    GBSBL NCHAR(8) NULL, -- Subledger - G/L
    GBCO NCHAR(5) NULL, -- Company
    GBAPYC DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Beginning Balance/PYE Forward
    GBAN01 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 01
    GBAN02 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 02
    GBAN03 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 03
    GBAN04 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 04
    GBAN05 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 05
    GBAN06 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 06
    GBAN07 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 07
    GBAN08 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 08
    GBAN09 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 09
    GBAN10 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 10
    GBAN11 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 11
    GBAN12 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 12
    GBAN13 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 13
    GBAN14 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Posting 14
    GBAPYN DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Prior Year Net Postings
    GBAWTD DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Week-to-Date
    GBBORG DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Original/Beginning Budget
    GBPOU DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Memo Budget Changes
    GBPC INT NULL, -- Percent Complete
    GBTKER DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Memo Commitment Changes
    GBBREQ DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Budget - Requested
    GBBAPR DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Budget - Approved
    GBMCU NCHAR(12) NULL, -- Business Unit
    GBOBJ NCHAR(6) NULL, -- Object Account
    GBSUB NCHAR(8) NULL, -- Subsidiary
    GBUSER NCHAR(10) NULL, -- User ID
    GBPID NCHAR(10) NULL, -- Program ID
    GBUPMJ DATE NULL, -- Date - Updated
    GBJOBN NCHAR(10) NULL, -- Work Station ID
    GBSBLT NCHAR(1) NULL, -- Subledger Type
    GBUPMT INT NULL, -- Time - Last Updated
    GBCRCD NCHAR(3) NULL, -- Currency Code - From
    GBCRCX NCHAR(3) NULL, -- Currency Code - Denominated In
    GBPRGF NCHAR(1) NULL, -- Purge Flag
    GBAND01 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 01
    GBAND02 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 02
    GBAND03 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 03
    GBAND04 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 04
    GBAND05 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 05
    GBAND06 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 06
    GBAND07 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 07
    GBAND08 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 08
    GBAND09 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 09
    GBAND10 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 10
    GBAND11 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 11
    GBAND12 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 12
    GBAND13 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL, -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 13
    GBAND14 DECIMAL(15,2) NULL -- Amount - Net Debit Posting 14
)
WITH
(
    DISTRIBUTION = HASH (GBAID),
    CLUSTERED COLUMNSTORE INDEX
)
GO
